#

Quinoa and Black Bean Stuffed Peppers

45 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

MexicanAmerican

Course:

Main DishVegetarian

Tags:

HealthyEasyQuickVegetarian

Description

Colorful bell peppers filled with a nutritious mix of quinoa, black beans, and spices, perfect for a healthy meal!

Ingredients

  • bell peppers: 4 large
  • quinoa: 1 cup
  • black beans: 1 can (15 oz) drained and rinsed
  • corn (frozen or canned): 1 cup
  • diced tomatoes: 1 can (15 oz)
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • chili powder: 1 tsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • cheese (optional): 1 cup shredded (for topping)
